data.description:
**ASSUMABLE LOAN 6.25% / CONTACT LENDER BRIAN BELL with Movement Mortgage at 720.447.9196** 
Home was purchased in Spring 2023, however, Sellers are being transferred out of State.

Stunning 4 bedroom, 3 bath Luxury Castle Rock Home with WALKOUT BASEMENT in The Meadows! Located on a quiet cul-de-sac with unbeatable mountain views, this 2 Story Home boasts 5144 Square Feet including the Unfinished Walk-Out Basement. From the moment you walk in the front door, you are welcomed with abundant natural lighting and beautiful hardwood floors.  The Living Room has a 3 sided glass fireplace, oversized mantle and floor to ceiling windows on each side. The Dining Area is perfectly situated for cozy dinners by the fire. This Kitchen is a Chef's Dream, featuring a Large Island with Eat-In Seating, Walk-In Pantry, Abundant Cabinets, Tons of Countertop Space, Stainless Steel Appliances and Granite Countertops. Flowing into the cozy Family Room you will find a second gas fireplace, built-ins, dramatic mountain views and large windows. Your expansive deck faces directly west and puts you front and center for some of the most spectacular views Castle Rock has to offer. This home was made for entertaining. Large Laundry Room has ample cabinets and is plumbed for a utility sink. 
The upper level offers a large Loft Area that is a great bonus space and center to the 4 bedrooms. Spacious Primary Suite with incredible spa-like bath, oversized shower, soaking tub, walk-in closet and all the luxury you are looking for! 3 additional Bedrooms all with walk-in closets and a full bath awaits you. 
The 1587 square foot unfinished Walkout Basement is ready for you to make it your own! 
4 CAR GARAGE!!! 3 Car plus 1 Car Tandem is every garage lovers dream! 
Access to The Grange Pool and Clubhouse, Bison Park, Ridgeline Open Space!!!
Welcome to The Meadows, Welcome Home!
